\c 2
\s Amadodana kaIsrayeli
\p
\v 1 La ngamadodana kaIsrayeli: ORubeni, uSimeyoni, uLevi, loJuda, uIsakari, loZebuluni,
\v 2 uDani, uJosefa, loBhenjamini, uNafithali, uGadi, loAsheri\x + Gen. 29.32. 30.5. 35.18,22. 46.8.\x*.
\s Inzalo kaJuda
\p
\v 3 Amadodana kaJuda: OEri loOnani loShela\x + Gen. 38.3-5. 46.12. Nani 26.19,20.\x*; amathathu wawazalelwa yindodakazi kaShuwa umKhananikazi\x + Gen. 38.2.\x*. Kodwa uEri izibulo likaJuda wayemubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*; yasimbulala\x + Gen. 38.7.\x*.
\v 4 UTamari, umalokozana wakhe, wasemzalela uPerezi loZera. Wonke amadodana kaJuda ayemahlanu\x + Gen. 38.29,30. Ruthe 4.12. Mat. 1.3.\x*.
\v 5 Amadodana kaPerezi: OHezironi loHamuli\x + Gen. 46.12. Ruthe 4.18.\x*.
\v 6 Njalo amadodana kaZera: OZimri loEthani\x + 1 Kho. 4.31.\x* loHemani\x + 1 Kho. 4.31.\x* loKalikoli\x + 1 Kho. 4.31.\x* loDara; wonke ayemahlanu.
\v 7 Njalo amadodana kaKarimi\x + Josh. 7.1.\x*: UAkari\x + Josh. 7.1.\x*, umhluphi kaIsrayeli, owenza isiphambeko ngokuqalekisiweyo\x + Josh. 6.18. 7.25.\x*.
\v 8 Njalo amadodana kaEthani: UAzariya.
\v 9 Njalo amadodana kaHezironi awazalelwayo: OJerameli\x + 1.25. 1 Sam. 27.10. 30.29.\x* loRamu\x + Ruthe 4.19,20. Mat. 1.4.\x* loKalebi.
\v 10 URamu wasezala uAminadaba\x + Ruthe 4.19,20. Mat. 1.4.\x*; uAminadaba wasezala uNahishoni\x + Nani 1.7. 2.3. Eks. 6.23.\x*\x + Ruthe 4.19,20. Mat. 1.4.\x* induna yabantwana bakoJuda\x + Nani 1.7. 2.3. Eks. 6.23.\x*.
\v 11 UNahishoni wasezala uSalima; uSalima wasezala uBhowazi\x + Ruthe 4.21,22.\x*;
\v 12 uBhowazi wasezala uObedi; uObedi wasezala uJese\x + Ruthe 4.21,22.\x*.
\p
\v 13 UJese wasezala izibulo lakhe uEliyabi\x + 27.18. 1 Sam. 16.6,8. 17.13.\x*, loAbinadaba owesibili, loShimeya owesithathu\x + 27.18. 1 Sam. 16.6,8. 17.13.\x*,
\v 14 uNethaneli owesine, uRadayi owesihlanu,
\v 15 uOzema owesithupha, uDavida owesikhombisa\x + 1 Sam. 16.10. 17.12,14.\x*.
\v 16 Odadewabo babengoZeruya loAbigayili. Lamadodana kaZeruya: OAbishayi loJowabi loAsaheli; abathathu\x + 2 Sam. 2.18.\x*.
\v 17 UAbigayili wasezala uAmasa; loyise kaAmasa wayenguJetheri umIshmayeli\x + 12.18. 2 Sam. 17.25.\x*.
\p
\v 18 UKalebi indodana kaHezironi wasezala kuAzuba umka\add khe\add* lakuJeriyothi; lala ngamadodana akhe: OJesheri loShobabi loAridoni\x + 2.9,42.\x*.
\v 19 UAzuba esefile uKalebi wazithathela uEfrathi owamzalela uHuri\x + 2.50.\x*.
\v 20 UHuri wasezala uUri\x + Eks. 17.10,12. 24.14.\x*; uUri wasezala uBhezaleli\x + Eks. 31.2.\x*.
\p
\v 21 Emva kwalokho uHezironi wasengena kundodakazi kaMakiri uyise kaGileyadi; wayithatha eseleminyaka engamatshumi ayisithupha. Yasimzalela uSegubi\x + Nani 27.1.\x*.
\v 22 USegubi wasezala uJayiri owayelemizi engamatshumi amabili lantathu elizweni leGileyadi.
\v 23 Wasethatha kibo iGeshuri leAramu kanye lemizana yeJayiri, kanye leKenathi lemizana yayo; imizi engamatshumi ayisithupha. Bonke labo babengamadodana kaMakiri uyise kaGileyadi\x + Nani 32.41,42. Dute. 3.14. Josh. 13.30.\x*.
\v 24 Lemva kokufa kukaHezironi eKalebi-Efratha\x + 2.19,50. 4.4.\x*, uAbhiya umkaHezironi wamzalela uAshuri\x + 4.5.\x* uyise kaThekhowa\x + 2 Sam. 14.2.\x*.
\p
\v 25 Njalo amadodana kaJerameli izibulo likaHezironi ayengoRamu izibulo, loBuna, loOreni, loOzema, uAhiya\x + 2.9.\x*.
\v 26 UJerameli laye wayelomunye umfazi obizo lakhe lalinguAthara; wayengunina kaOnama.
\v 27 Njalo amadodana kaRamu izibulo likaJerameli ayengoMahazi loJamini loEkeri.
\v 28 Lamadodana kaOnama ayengoShamayi loJada. Lamadodana kaShamayi: ONadabi loAbhishuri.
\v 29 Lebizo lomkaAbhishuri lalinguAbihayili, owamzalela oAhibani loMolidi.
\v 30 Njalo amadodana kaNadabi: OSeledi loAphayimi; kodwa uSeledi wafa engelabantwana.
\v 31 Njalo amadodana kaAphayimi: UIshi. Lamadodana kaIshi: USheshani. Lamadodana kaSheshani: UAhilayi\x + 2.35.\x*.
\v 32 Njalo amadodana kaJada umfowabo kaShamayi: OJetheri loJonathani; kodwa uJetheri wafa engelabantwana\x + 2.28.\x*.
\v 33 Njalo amadodana kaJonathani: OPelethi loZaza. Laba babengabantwana bakaJerameli.
\p
\v 34 Njalo uSheshani wayengelamadodana, kodwa amadodakazi; njalo uSheshani wayelenceku, umGibhithe, obizo layo lalinguJariha.
\v 35 USheshani wasenika uJariha inceku yakhe indodakazi yakhe yaba ngumka\add khe\add*; yasimzalela uAthayi\x + 2.35.\x*.
\v 36 UAthayi wasezala uNathani, uNathani wasezala uZabadi\x + 11.41.\x*,
\v 37 uZabadi wasezala uEfilali, uEfilali wasezala uObedi\x + 2 Lan. 23.1.\x*,
\v 38 uObedi wasezala uJehu, uJehu wasezala uAzariya\x + 2 Lan. 23.1.\x*,
\v 39 uAzariya wasezala uHelezi, uHelezi wasezala uEleyasa,
\v 40 uEleyasa wasezala uSisimayi, uSisimayi wasezala uShaluma,
\v 41 uShaluma wasezala uJekamiya, uJekamiya wasezala uElishama\x + 2 Kho. 25.25. Jer. 36.12,21.\x*.
\p
\v 42 Njalo amadodana kaKalebi umfowabo kaJerameli\x + 2.9,18.\x*: OMesha, izibulo lakhe, onguyise kaZifi\x + 4.16. Josh. 15.55.\x*, lamadodana kaMaresha\x + 4.21. Josh. 15.44.\x* uyise kaHebroni\x + Josh. 15.54.\x*.
\v 43 Njalo amadodana kaHebroni: OKora loTapuwa loRekemi loShema\x + Josh. 15.53.\x*.
\v 44 UShema wasezala uRahama uyise kaJorikeyamu; uRekemi wasezala uShamayi.
\v 45 Lendodana kaShamayi: UMawoni\x + 4.16. Josh. 15.55.\x*; loMawoni wayenguyise kaBeti-Zuri\x + 2 Lan. 11.7.\x*.
\v 46 UEfa umfazi omncinyane kaKalebi wasezala oHarani loMoza loGazezi; uHarani wasezala uGazezi.
\v 47 Njalo amadodana kaJahidayi: ORegema loJothamu loGeshani loPeleti loEfa loShahafi\x + Josh. 15.27.\x*.
\v 48 UMahaka umfazi omncinyane kaKalebi wazala oSheberi loTirihana.
\v 49 Wasezala uShahafi uyise kaMadimana\x + Josh. 15.31. Isa. 10.31.\x*, uSheva uyise kaMakibena, loyise kaGibeya\x + Josh. 15.57.\x*. Lendodakazi kaKalebi yayinguAkisa\x + Josh. 15.17. Hlu. 1.13.\x*.
\p
\v 50 Laba babengabantwana bakaKalebi, indodana kaHuri\x + 2.19.\x*, izibulo likaEfratha: OShobhali, uyise kaKiriyathi-Jeyarimi\x + Josh. 15.9.\x*,
\v 51 uSalima uyise kaBhethelehema\x + 4.4. Gen. 35.19.\x*, uHarefi uyise kaBeti-Gaderi.
\v 52 UShobhali uyise kaKiriyathi-Jeyarimi wayelamadodana: UHarowe, ingxenye yamaMenuhothi.
\v 53 Njalo insendo zikaKiriyathi-Jeyarimi: AmaIthiri\x + 2 Sam. 23.38.\x* lamaPuti lamaShumathi lamaMishrayi; kwaphuma kuwo amaZorathi\x + 4.2. Josh. 15.33.\x* lamaEshitawoli\x + 4.2. Josh. 15.33.\x*.
\v 54 Amadodana kaSalima\x + 2.51.\x*: OBhethelehema\x + 4.4. Gen. 35.19.\x*, lamaNetofa\x + 2 Kho. 25.23.\x*, uAtarothi, uBeti-Jowabi, lengxenye yamaManahethi\x + 2.52.\x*, amaZori\x + 4.2. Josh. 15.33.\x*.
\v 55 Lensendo zababhali ababehlala eJabezi\x + 4.9,10.\x*, amaTirathi, amaShimeyathi, amaSukathi. Labo babengamaKeni avela kuHamathi\x + Hlu. 1.16. Josh. 15.57.\x* uyise wendlu kaRekabi\x + 2 Kho. 10.15. Jer. 35.2.\x*.